From: FleetFlow Lead <lead@fleetflow.local>
Date: Fri, 15 May 2026 04:13:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: scaffold v2 with green build (StripeEvent model, auth
 routes, lazy clients)

- prisma schema: add StripeEvent model for webhook idempotency
- app: add /, /login, /signup, (dashboard)/layout, root layout w/ ClerkProvider
- lib/storage: lazy S3 client init so missing env doesn't break next build
- api/stripe/webhook: lazy Stripe client init, no apiVersion (uses dashboard pin)
- api/loads: explicit type narrowing on zod-parsed query params
- api/loads/[id]/status: cast current.status to LoadStatus for transitions lookup
- lib/auth/tenancy: explicit param types on all 12 Prisma extension callbacks
- instrumentation + sentry configs: stubbed (uncomment after npm i @sentry/nextjs)
- add tsconfig, next.config.mjs, tailwind.config, postcss.config, globals.css, next-env

Verified: tsc --noEmit clean, next build green, next dev boots in 854ms.
